      <title>随着出生率下降，中国许多医院停止新生儿接生服务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/many-hospitals-china-stop-newborn-delivery-services-birth-rate-drops-2024-03-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体《每日经济新闻》报道，中国许多医院今年已停止提供新生儿接生服务，行业专家警告称，由于新生儿数量创纪录下降，需求下降，将导致“产科寒冬”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/many-hospitals-china-stop-newborn-delivery-services-birth-rate-drops-2024-03-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 07:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
